{"tid":2263651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥長青店舖遭淋紅油 唔擔心人身安全：咁多警察使乜驚","createTime":"2020-10-30T05:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:06:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":367,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b772d366adf83ea5005f28dcccb7a3e6d4a8bd5e","tid":2263651,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"麥包返回店前，《蘋果》上前訪問，麥包心情輕鬆，問到他的店上周被淋紅油事件可有新進展？麥包說：「交咗畀警方處理，我唔知。」可擔心再被滋擾？麥包答：「唔擔心，我行得正企得正，其他嘢交畀警方。」至於人身安全，他說：「唔怕，香港係法治社會，咁多警察使乜驚。」麥包表示即使發生這件事，但店中生意不受影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201029/FKRU6WAKPZGXZFVBRU5ITFX5VQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201029%2FFKRU6WAKPZGXZFVBRU5ITFX5VQ%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=20c31afa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201029%2FFKRU6WAKPZGXZFVBRU5ITFX5VQ%2F&h=95fb48e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201029/FKRU6WAKPZGXZFVBRU5ITFX5VQ/</a>"},{"pid":"63a800976dcc6b00ab2b1d563122961cf23a9642","tid":2263651,"uid":40272,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"商界燈神"},{"pid":"aaadd61ca8645abd9746c5d198949074550dc3b9","tid":2263651,"uid":185656,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"希望佢投考警甴"},{"pid":"3989dd8fc285ba3c3d026bbe23ba71c6785acb33","tid":2263651,"uid":37528,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"正宗垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48833d34f6c66f31c2e7fc5c1d27d203c0bb98e4","tid":2263651,"uid":7436,"like":144,"dislike":2,"score":142,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:07:46.000Z","msg":"條友係咪行衰運, 好似搞乜衰乜"},{"pid":"3c372df9be3aef12881c5cdfd73acea4261abb98","tid":2263651,"uid":89382,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202